data.description: Experience the height of elegance in this stunning two-story home fronting Dawn View Park. This expansive residence boasts a frontyard with turf and park views. Inside, the open floorplan creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere. The cozy living room is perfect for relaxation, while the gorgeous kitchen features granite countertops, a center island, wood cabinetry, a pantry, and stainless steel appliances. With four bedrooms, including a huge master suite with a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom with double vanity sinks, walk-in shower, and bathtub, comfort is guaranteed. Additional highlights include a utility room, attached garage at the back, and a covered patio. Don't miss out on this exquisite home in a picturesque location!
